            <h2>Meetings</h2>
            <p>We would love to see you at any of our gatherings. Whether you are a regular churchgoer
            or simply curious, you are very welcome at Cathcart United Free Church.</p>

            <!-- SUNDAY -->
            <div class="section-card" id="sunday">
                <div class="section-card-header">
                    <h3>Sunday at 11</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="section-card-body">
                    <p>We meet together in the church and on Zoom every Sunday from
                    <strong>11:00am to 12:15pm</strong>. Our Sunday gathering is the heart of our week
                    together — a time to worship God, explore the Bible, pray and sing. Whether you are
                    joining us in person or online, you are warmly welcome.</p>

                    <p>After the service there is tea and coffee, and plenty of opportunity to chat and
                    get to know each other. We are a friendly congregation and nobody need feel they
                    are on their own.</p>

