                    <h4>Join Us on Zoom or YouTube</h4>
                    <p>We also livestream our Sunday service on our
                    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@cathcartufchurch7834/videos"
                    target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube channel</a>.
                    To join us on Zoom please
                    <a href="contact.html">contact us by email</a>
                    and we will send you the details.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- MIDWEEK -->
            <div class="section-card" id="midweek">
                <div class="section-card-header">
                    <h3>Midweek — Time for Reflection</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="section-card-body">
                    <p>Every Wednesday at <strong>10:30am</strong> we gather in the church building for
                    a quiet 40-minute reflective time together. This is a gentler, more contemplative
                    gathering — a space to pause mid-week and reconnect with God.</p>

                    <p>Each session includes a Bible reading, a short talk and music. This gathering is
                    in-person only, which adds to its intimate and unhurried character. All are welcome.</p>

